520
00:27:12,540 --> 00:27:13,780
came together,

521
00:27:14,220 --> 00:27:15,700
she became heartbroken.

522
00:27:15,820 --> 00:27:16,700
Sister...

523
00:27:18,940 --> 00:27:19,780
Suddenly,

524
00:27:19,860 --> 00:27:21,020
she shed a tear

525
00:27:21,780 --> 00:27:23,460
