526
00:27:25,860 --> 00:27:27,460
What's worse,

527
00:27:28,100 --> 00:27:29,940
the bigger you grew in her womb,

528
00:27:30,620 --> 00:27:31,940
the weaker she became.

529
00:27:32,740 --> 00:27:33,580
Sister,

530
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:35,140
