538
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:48,220
You can't take the risk!

539
00:27:48,500 --> 00:27:49,700
I have to.

540
00:27:53,740 --> 00:27:55,220
If you can't do it,

541
00:27:55,860 --> 00:27:57,580
I'll do it for you.

542
00:28:02,620 --> 00:28:03,460
Sister,

543
00:28:04,060 --> 00:28:05,300
