546
00:28:10,900 --> 00:28:12,020
I have to protect him.

547
00:28:24,460 --> 00:28:27,060
Please don't leave me!

548
00:28:36,580 --> 00:28:38,140
When she gave birth to you,

549
00:28:40,340 --> 00:28:42,580
