566
00:29:32,260 --> 00:29:34,180
But she loved you so much.

567
00:29:35,700 --> 00:29:37,500
She only cared about you.

568
00:29:39,180 --> 00:29:40,620
Why did she abandon me?

569
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:43,260
I remember

